title: Electrolux Dishwasher Lower Rack Assembly
description: Electrolux Dishwasher Lower Rack Assembly ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 16 Reviews PartSelect Number PS17219606 Manufacturer Part Number 5304535253 This lower dishrack assembly comes with 8 rollers enabling it to roll in and out with ease. The dishrack is approximately 22 inches long x 20 inches wide. The dishrack holds dishes in place during the dishwashing cycle. If you see rust spots on the dishes, the lower rack will not pull out, or the lower rack is visibly rusted or damaged, the part should be replaced. Other common symptoms include: unusual or loud noises coming from the unit, or the dishes on the lower rack not being washed properly. This part is also known as a dish rack or a dishwasher rack.

installationInstructions.author: Deb from MARIA STEIN, OH
installationInstructions.title: Needed to replace some racks that were rusted and coming apart
installationInstructions.content: All we had to do was remove the old racks and pop in the new. Very easy to do!
